articles.title: Carrie Underwood Performs, a Cappella, at President Trump’s Inauguration — Watch Video and Weigh In - TVLine
articles.description: Carrie Underwood was among those who performed at President Trump's inauguration on Monday, with an unplanned a cappella 'America the Beautiful."
articles.content: An eclectic mix of performers assembled Monday in Washington, D.C., for President Donald Trump‘s inauguration, with Carrie Underwood among the biggest names serenading him back into the Oval Office.… [+1531 chars]
